rows.label: bf05260100_0010
rows.name: Whew, it's cold this morning...

rows.label: bf05260100_0020
rows.name: Fan-san...?

rows.label: bf05260100_0030
rows.name:
What's up?
Are you captivated by an adult woman's charm~?

rows.label: bf05260100_0040
rows.name: Nia, why are you here?

rows.label: bf05260100_0050
rows.name: I'm an early riser, you know.

rows.label: bf05260100_0060
rows.name:
Hmm, so that's what it is.
I'll tell Homura and Hikari.

rows.label: bf05260100_0070
rows.name:
I-it's not like that!
Just...

rows.label: bf05260100_0080
rows.name: "Just" what?

rows.label: bf05260100_0090
rows.name: I just thought she looked sad.

rows.label: bf05260100_0100
rows.name:
Oh? Rex-sama, Nia-sama.
There's still some time until the audience.

rows.label: bf05260100_0110
rows.name: We just woke up a bit early.

rows.label: bf05260100_0120
rows.name: Ah, I see.

rows.label: bf05260100_0130
rows.name: But this mural is really impressive.

rows.label: bf05260100_0140
rows.name: It depicts the creation of Alst.

rows.label: bf05260100_0150
rows.name:
It was apparently painted long ago,
when this country was just formed.

rows.label: bf05260100_0160
rows.name: You've been looking at it for a while...

rows.label: bf05260100_0170
rows.name: ...They're not there.

rows.label: bf05260100_0180
rows.name: What's not there?

rows.label: bf05260100_0190
rows.name: Memories...

rows.label: bf05260100_0200
rows.name:
I should have existed in this world
since the time this mural was painted, but...

rows.label: bf05260100_0210
rows.name: I don't have memories from that time.

rows.label: bf05260100_0220
rows.name: ...Because you're a Blade.

rows.label: bf05260100_0230
rows.name: Who I was with, what I was doing...

rows.label: bf05260100_0240
rows.name: I want to know that.

rows.label: bf05260100_0250
rows.name:
Hikari has also lived a long time, so maybe
she might know something about you.

rows.label: bf05260100_0260
rows.name: Hikari-sama called me "Kasumi."

rows.label: bf05260100_0270
rows.name:
Maybe I might have met Hikari-sama
somewhere before...

rows.label: bf05260100_0280
rows.name: Shall we ask her after the audience is over?

rows.label: bf05260100_0290
rows.name:
Really?
Thank you, Rex-sama.

rows.label: bf05260100_0300
rows.name:
N-no, it's fine.
You helped us too.

rows.label: bf05260100_0310
rows.name:
Why are you blushing?
I'll really tell on you, seriously.

rows.label: bf05260100_0320
rows.name:
Wha-!
It's really not like that!

rows.label: bf05260100_0330
rows.name: I wonder about that~
